observations.managementAction:
A Memorandum was issued requiring the Municipal Accountant and General Services Office to maintain PPELC and PC for each category of assets whenever feasible and practicable;
EO has been issued creating an Inventory Committee and to conduct physical inventory of property, plant and equipment and to submit an inventory report which reconciled with the records of the Accounting Office;
A Memo was  issued to GSO, Municipal Treasurer and Municipal Accountant to exert extra effort in retrieving the supporting documents evidencing ownership of the recorded parcel of lands and facilitate the immediate registration and titling of the several  lots in the name of the Municipality; and 
 A Memo was  issued effecting the recording of the unbooked parcels of land with TCT under the name of the Municipality on the basis of the assessed value/s.
